## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- None (UI-only changes)

### Manual Verification
- Open app in Chrome DevTools > Toggle Device Toolbar
- Test at: 375px (iPhone SE), 414px (iPhone XR), 768px (iPad), 1280px (desktop)
- Navigate: Home → Property Detail → My Ads → Favorites → Admin → Membership
- Test hamburger menu open/close on mobile

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The Admin Dashboard sidebar-to-tab-bar conversion is the most complex change. The sidebar will collapse to a horizontal scrollable tab strip on mobile.
